<br>
I know Spell casting Fury gives us critical hits on DD spells, but how do they work on AoE's?<br>
<br>
Is it even possible to crit on aoe's?<br>
<br>
If you do land a crit while casting an aoe does it crit on all mobs hit? <br>
<br>
Or can you just crit on a single mob hit while the others get normal damage?<br>
<br>
<br>
If anybody has personal experience with these questions please add some insite.<br>
<br>
Thanks in advance,<br>
Bodhivista 55 druid of Xev <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usobesilvertree.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sobe Silvertree</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/misc_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Administrator</span><br> <font color=#333399>(12/22/01 8:43:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovegeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26195.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://people.ne.mediaone.net/sobe1/tag.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How do crits work on AoE spells?</span><hr size=1> Yes - Every Rain, meaning out of the 3 hits, a crit or more can land. <p><hr><body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" link="#FFFF00" vlink="#00FF00" alink="#00FF00"><div align="center"><center><table border="3" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#008080" bordercolordark="#000000" bordercolorlight="#008080"><tr><td valign="top" width="100%" background="http://people.ne.mediaone.net/sobe1/back.gif"><p align="center"><font color="#80FF00" size="4" face="Trebuchet MS"><strong>Sobe Silvertree</strong></font><font color="#FFFF80" face="Trebuchet MS"><br></font><font color="#FFFF80" size="2" face="Trebuchet MS">"</font><a href="http://www.afterlifeguild.org/members.cgi?page=details&character=Sobe" target="new"><font color="#FFFF80" size="2" face="Trebuchet MS">The Wanderer</font></a><font color="#FFFF80" size="2" face="Trebuchet MS">" and "</font><a href="http://www.geocities.com/kibadachi_uk/epiclink.htm" target="new"><font color="#FFFF80" size="2" face="Trebuchet MS">1st Tunarian Protector</font></a><font color="#FFFF80" size="2" face="T