spells like lighting blast.<br>
<br>
I decided to bite the bullet and check it out so I put two alt points into the first level of Spell Casting Fury.<br>
<br>
I was quading Raptors and killed about 40, thats about 40*8=320 individual hits.  I hadn't gotten a single crit and I was getting sorta mad.  Then I was fooling around and killed a raptor using Scoriae and got a crit for 917.  I was happy to get a crit but I thought that was proff positive that I couldn't get crits using my aoe's.<br>
<br>
Then a few quads later I got two crits in a row using Lighting Blast!  I did a little happy dance.  =)<br>
<br>
The 2% chance to land a critical blast while casting with this skill isn't much as you can see, but the visual gratification is great for moral support and its fun to have others ooo and aaah at the numbers.<br>
<br>
<br>
Bodhi<br>
